% ====================================================================
% test_bestagon_proto_render_gate.trx -- run examples/bestagon-proto/
% proto-render-gate.trx self-test via the standard tests/ harness.
% ====================================================================
%
% Thin wrapper: loads proto-render-gate.trx (Phase 0.6B: 5x9 flat-top
% hex renderer per GDD section A.7), which auto-runs its self-test on
% load.  We just need to confirm the test reached its end without
% throwing.
%
% Asserts:
%   - section A.7.1 empty 7-hex diamond reproduces byte-for-byte
%   - section A.7.2 terrain mix reproduces byte-for-byte
%   - section A.7.3 unit formation reproduces byte-for-byte
%   - section A.7.0 canvas dimension (23 wide x 13 tall) matches
%
% Runs on default 1 MB VM.
% ====================================================================

(examples/bestagon-proto/proto-render-gate.trx) run
(__test_ok__) =
